section.text:
(a) the term “Contracting Party” means
                    the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region or the Kingdom of Norway, as the
                    context requires;

(b) the term “person” includes a
                    corporation, a partnership, a trust or any other body of persons, whether
                    incorporated or unincorporated;

subsection.text:
(B) in the case of Norway, any enterprise which, under the laws of
                        Norway, is liable to tax therein by reason of domicile, residence, place of
                        management or any other criterion of a similar nature;

section.text:
(d) the term “international traffic”
                    means any transport by a ship, except when the ship is operated solely between
                    places in the area of the other Contracting Party;

part.text:
for any year of assessment beginning on or
                after 1 April in the calendar year next following that in which notice is
                given;
